Here is a multiple choice question in JSON format. Answer it based on the choices provided.

{
    "question": "Consider the following Python class definition:\\n\\n```python\\nclass Employee:\\n    def __init__(self, name, id):\\n        self.name = name\\n        self.id = id\\n\\ndef setName(self, new_name):\\n    self.name = new_name\\n```\\nAssuming that e1 is an instance of Employee, which of the following lines of code is correct for changing the name of the Employee instance, e1, to 'John'?",
    "choices": [
        {
            "choice": "e1.name = 'John'"
        },
        {
            "choice": "e1.setName('John')"
        },
        {
            "choice": "setName(e1, 'John')"
        }
    ]
}
